  fiber: 1 g
  sodium: 1290 mg
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/smoky-bbq-chicken-sandwiches-65aff405a33a91ae6a3f7e73
time required: 10 minutes
author: HelloFresh
